citeinfo.title: Senate District Boundaries, Minnesota, 1994

descript.abstract: This is a polygon data set of the historical 1994 Senate District Boundaries. It displays district numbers. It was derived from U.S. Census Bureau 1990 TIGER/Line files as a result of redistricting efforts.
descript.purpose: This data was created to display historical 1994 Senate District boundaries and to allow geographical review/analysis adhereing to the 1994 MN Senate District boundaries.

browse.browsed: Statewide view of Senate District Boundaries

timeperd.current: This file is outdated as of 2000 and 2010 Census Bureau redistricting efforts. Boundary updates are completed every decennial census.

procstep.procdesc: This database of Senate District Boundaries was developed from U.S. Census Bureau 1990 TIGER/Line files. The redistricting boundaries were extracted from the 1990 TIGER/Line files using Maptitude software. This was completed by dissolving census block boundaries to the established senate district boundaries.
